data.title: Start a free trial of GitLab Gold - no credit card required :rocket:
data.description:
At any point while using the free version of GitLab you can start a trial of GitLab Gold for free for 30 days. With a GitLab Gold trial, you'll get access to all of the most popular features across all of the paid tiers within GitLab. 
 
:white_check_mark: Reduce risk by requiring team leaders to approve merge requests.
 
:white_check_mark: Ensure code quality with Multiple code reviews.
 
:white_check_mark: Run your CI pipelines for up to 50,000 minutes (~9,500 CI builds).
 
:white_check_mark: Plan and organize parallel development with multiple issue boards.
  
:white_check_mark: Report on the productivity of each team in your organization by using issue analytics. 
 
:white_check_mark: Dynamically scan Docker images for vulnerabilities before production pushes. 
 
:white_check_mark: Scan security vulnerabilities, license compliance and dependencies in your CI pipelines. 
 
:white_check_mark: Get alerted when your application performance degrades. 
 
:white_check_mark: And so much more, [you can view all the features here](https://about.gitlab.com/pricing/gitlab-com/feature-comparison/). 
 
## Next steps
* [ ] [Click here to start a trial of GitLab Gold.](https://gitlab.com/-/trial_registrations/new?glm_content=user_onboarding_whats_in_paid_tiers&glm_source=gitlab.com)
